Package: bambamR
Title: End-to-End RNA-Seq Processing from FASTQ to Publication-Ready Plots
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Raban", "Heller",
           email = "raban.heller@uni-ulm.de",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8006-9742")),
    person("Hanno", "Witte", role = "aut"),
    person("Konrad", "Steinestel", role = "aut")
    )
Description: A streamlined toolkit for RNA-seq analysis covering FASTQ/BAM
    import, quality control, alignment, read counting, normalization,
    differential expression analysis, and publication-ready visualizations
    including onco plots, volcano plots, heatmaps, and PCA. Operates in
    minimal mode with CRAN-only dependencies or in full mode when
    Bioconductor packages are available.
